message.content:
Contacting Customers

Responding to Inquiries

1. I will promptly respond to customer inquiries via phone, email, or mail, ensuring that their concerns are addressed in a timely and professional manner. 2. I will actively listen to the customer's issue, ask clarifying questions, and provide clear and concise information to resolve their inquiry.

Notifying Customers of Claim Investigation Results

1. I will notify customers of the investigation results in a clear and concise manner, providing detailed information about the findings and any subsequent actions. 2. I will ensure that customers are informed of any additional information or documentation required to complete the investigation.

Notifying Customers of Planned Adjustments

1. I will proactively notify customers of any planned adjustments or changes to their policies or claims, providing adequate notice and explanation of the changes. 2. I will offer support and guidance to customers affected by the changes, ensuring a smooth transition.
